        "subject": "LU-1965 build: Compilation broken with --disable-liblustre",
        "message": "LU-1965 build: Compilation broken with --disable-liblustre\n\nAdded compile-time 'if LIBLUSTRE' checks before explicitely referring\nto libcfs. This fixes a regression introduced by commit\nbfb38a047e0fc12e68a7aa3a2d2ec7a6e9d696ed that prevented compilation to\nsucceed with --disable-liblustre.\n\nSigned-off-by: Henri Doreau <henri.doreau@cea.fr>\nChange-Id: I0484327cc69fa0ed5b25ee72bb3d7ae7eef9eb69\n"
      },
